I tell you, in the name of Jesus, you're

02:25:46.080 --> 02:25:47.750
coming out of that hell. You're going to

02:25:47.760 --> 02:25:50.309
get born again.

02:25:50.319 --> 02:25:52.630
Hey, it could happen and I believe it

02:25:52.640 --> 02:25:55.590
will happen.

02:25:55.600 --> 02:25:58.150
We love you all. Remember: put a smile

02:25:58.160 --> 02:26:01.830
on your face and a song in your heart.

02:26:01.840 --> 02:26:03.990
Jesus loves you and we love you. God

02:26:04.000 --> 02:26:06.230
bless you all. Have a wonderful evening.

02:26:06.240 --> 02:26:10.200
Sleep well. Bye-bye.

